Files content and chronological order
-------------------------------------
Edite September 27, 2016


 1) interpolate_population.R   
    Create layers of population (5Km) 2001-2004, 2006-2009, 2011-2014 by interpolating
    the available data 2000, 2005, 2010, 2015
    
 2) binomial_model.stan    
    Binomial regression model in rstan
 
 3) binomial_sampler.stan    
    Binomial samples generator in rstan

 4) country_stats.R 
    Compute electricity access and households size per country

 5) household_rasters.R   
    Create layers of number of households (5Km) 2001-2015.
    Divide pixel-population by average number of household members per country.
    
 6) z_covariates.R   
    Create layers of standardized covariates for the geostatistical model.
    lit, zntl, zhouse, zpop
    
 7) dhs_preprocess.R
    Clean DHS surveys and organize them in a data frame
    
 8) additional_surveys_preprocess.R
    Put surveys, appart form DHS, in a data frame
    
 9) third_set_surveys.R
    Put third set of surveys in a data frame
    
10) dhs_w_covariates.R
    Add covariates to data frame with DHS data
    
11) other_data_w_covariates.R
    Add covariates to data frame with additional surveys
    
12) set3_w_covariates.R
    Add covariates to set3
    
13) combine_datasets.R
    Merge DHS surveys and set 3
    
14) inla_preliminaries.R
    Define mesh and data indices
  
15) core_model_w_latent_pred.R
    Code for running INLA